prefuse.visual

Interface EdgeItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Edge, Tuple, VisualItem
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TableEdgeItem

    public interface EdgeItem
extends VisualItem, Edge
    VisualItem that represents an edge in a graph. This interface combines the VisualItem interface with the Edge interface.
    Author:
    jeffrey heer
